But seriously, bouncing ideas around couldn't hurt, except as has been pointed out, we are a small server and nothing is likely to change for quite some time. I hope they don't consider us a failed experiment, because I like it like it is now. It's kind of a pain sometimes, but it is more of a challenge and the people who are here want to be here. <p>Palantiri, Ranger of Norrath<BR>Sacred Jesters Of Quellious, Woodfellas<BR>Cosmos Mariner, Destination Unknown<BR>www.angelfire.com/games2/NNB/ <BR><BR>Dohneagle of Firiona Vie<BR><BR>Why is it that every MOB you are hunting is never found unless you are on a corpse run, when they are at every turn?<BR>



